create table tbl_geo_location_value (ID int ,longitude varchar(255),latitude varchar(255),elevation varchar(255))
create table tbl_historical_data (ID int ,date_current datetime,hour_current int,minute_current int,temperature varchar(255),humidity varchar(255),station_name varchar(255))
